RSA 101 Puzzle

With every problem you solve, you'll receive a piece of the puzzle.
Put it together and see the big picture!
The puzzle pieces are encrypted with AES, so don't cheat!
                                  Encrypted piece
                                         |
subflag -[SHA256]➝ 256 bit key --[AES decryption]➝ Piece image
